This application was developed by HND 37 student. student No E163390. All rights reserved (2022).
This application is fully capable of managing the data of Poly Pipe Company. The Main Menu is the Navigator of this Application. After the login form main menu will be displayed.
staff management - this will direct the user to staff management dashboard
job management - this will direct user to job management window
equipment management - this allows to add or remove equipments to the system
customer management - this will direct user to the customer dashboard
All buttons will change or call the data of the Sql database. The warning messages will appear when deleting a record, and leaving a dashboard.
